yhedron with four faces</div>
<div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be co=
nfused with <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetraedron" title=3D"T=
etraedron">Tetraedron</a> or <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetra=
