<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Circumradius">Circumradius<=
/h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[=
</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DTetrahedron&=
amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D16" title=3D"Edit section: Circumradius"><s=
