ub>3</sub></span> can be formulated as matrix-vector product:<sup id=3D"cit=
e_ref-34" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetr=
ahedron#cite_note-34"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>33<span class=3D=
"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
