er/svg/d928ec15aeef83aade867992ee473933adb6139d" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:5.656ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle n=
=3D4}"></span> in both <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomson_pro=
blem" title=3D"Thomson problem">Thomson problem</a> (concerning the minimum=
-energy configuration of <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-i=
nline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D=
